{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/commit/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"f467daa4-1c98-5deb-bd6f-f059c7b43732","html":"<style>\n.loader {\n  border-radius: 100%;\n  height: 250px;\n  width: 250px;\n}\n</style>\n<p>Commit is a sales forecasting capture tool that replaces manual forecasting processes. It gathers and displays committed opportunities in one place.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ca9f1a2104d6eb93edc3db2a682a7513/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"Home page\"\n        src=\"/static/ca9f1a2104d6eb93edc3db2a682a7513/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ca9f1a2104d6eb93edc3db2a682a7513/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/ca9f1a2104d6eb93edc3db2a682a7513/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Home page</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>In this project, I was in charge of restyling most part of the front-end and I helped to another co-worker to build the rest of it.</p>\n<p>From a UI perspective, Commit is quite a straight-forward app. Perhaps, one of the most interesting aspects, would be the animated SVG radial charts that I had to build for the summary section in the header. The rest of the UI is just composed of a tabs component with a table on each tab, a top nav with several drop-downs and some colorful boxes. The app is also fully responsive.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\n  <img class=\"loader\" src=\"/f8539d350c8c30254523ce6b2bacd5ce/loader.gif\" alt=\"laoder\">\n</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2017"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Commit","categories":"vodafone react redux webpack web inverted","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/68df40b8102ef20e6f88f2b682bc8eed/f3583/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/commit/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}